'''Compugoal Technical College''' is a [[Private university|private]] college located in [[Nairobi]], [[Kenya]]. The college was founded by Mr.Patrick.M. Mulwa and Mr.Jignesh Karsan in 1996, and offers Class courses and Distance Learning in computer Science, Business Studies, Hospitality Management, Tourism management and Languages (German, Spanish, Italian, [[Standard Chinese|Mandarin]], French, English and [[Swahili language|Swahili]]).

==Affiliation==
Compugoal Technical College is located Nairobi Central Business District and duly registered and approved by TVETA under the Ministry of Education and affiliated to the following examination bodies: ICM-UK, [[City and Guilds of London Institute|City and Guilds]], [[Kenya National Examination Council]] (KNEC), Association of Business Executives (ABE-UK), ABMA, NITA, ICDL,KASNEB and IATA.

